description.text:
Have  you ever been in the kitchen and made a mess? The better question may actually be: when have you ever been in the kitchen and not made a mess? This handy broom and pan make for easy clean up in the kitchen. It has the brilliant design that allows it to have the cleanup power of a regular-sized dust pan with the convenience of just reaching to your fridge. Don't fret about the mess. Just use the &quot;Mini-Broom &amp; Dust Pan!&quot;  
This dust pan can be stored in any drawer or can be attached to a fridge with the addition of a magnet. The brush and dust pan also snap together for even easier storage!  
Here is a video of the dust pan in action: <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mNIj3x1sEL4" >https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mNIj3x1sEL4</a>

